{
  "stem": "15540.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father had been designated to collect the money that, that was asked for, for, for the transported across.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he went on to meet with the skipper, and we were lying there in the bushes until it got dark.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And meanwhile, my father had expressed to the people who had arranged the boat his worry about my cousin, who was three years younger than me, that he wasn't going to be able to walk this way.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And these people very nicely rode their bikes back and picked up my cousin, my two cousins, and brought them out on the bikes.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they joined us down on the beach where we were.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that night, a boat did appear.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we knew very little about anything, except that this, this boat was coming.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were just told to be very quiet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when we were given the word to get on board, and it started to rain, and we were given the word, we all got on board.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there was a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We ended up being 24 people on this little fishing boat which was meant for three.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And everybody just did what they were told and got down very quietly, and the boat took off.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was at night, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It started about 7 o'clock at night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By then, it's dark in Denmark in October already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that point, all of these people obviously knew what was going on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the fishermen were just fabulous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One of the men especially-- my brother remembers this better than I-- they called him the Lemon, and-- in Danish, and he was one of the well-known freedom fighters.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was taken by the Germans and shot.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
